  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6312551">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6312551/" class="title-link">坚韧质朴的老秦人，中华文明的浓缩之魂</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6312551"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/sl19910727/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u51551898-10.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sl19910727/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">霜月落</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-10-04"
      class="main-meta">2013-10-04 14:27:25</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6312551_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  几年前曾经在大学里看过黄健中导演的《大秦帝国之裂变》，这部让我反复看了3遍的电视剧给我留下了极为深刻的印象，至今是我认为所看过的最好的历史剧。如今开读孙皓晖的原著，激动期盼之余也夹杂着一丝膜拜之情。 秦国自战国以来就中原各国贬称为“西陲蛮夷”“虎狼之邦”，统...

